grid.arrange(gh1,gh2,gh3,gh4, gh5,gh6, gh7, gh8, gh9,gh10, ncol=3)

Relationship between energy and loudness

gg <-ggplot(df, aes(x=energy, y=loudness)) + 
  geom_point(aes(col=hit), size=1) + 
  geom_smooth(method="lm", col="firebrick", size=1) + 
  labs(title="Relationship between energy and loudness")

plot <- ggMarginal(gg, type = "density", fill="Grey")
plot

Relationship between energy and acousticness

gg2 <-ggplot(df, aes(x=energy, y=acousticness)) + 
  geom_point(aes(col=hit), size=1) + 
  geom_smooth(method="lm", col="firebrick", size=1) + 
  labs(title="Relationship between energy and acousticness")
ggMarginal(gg2, type = "density", fill="Grey")

Relationship between instrumentalness and loudness

gg3 <-ggplot(df, aes(x=instrumentalness, y=loudness)) + 
  geom_point(aes(col=hit), size=1) + 
  geom_smooth(method="lm", col="firebrick", size=1) + 
  labs(title="Relationship between instrumentalness and loudness")
ggMarginal(gg3, type = "density", fill="Grey")
